title: FC Bazenheid
text:
FC Bazenheid is a <a href="Association%20football">football</a> team based in <a href="Bazenheid">Bazenheid</a>, <a href="Switzerland">Switzerland</a>. They play in the <a href="2.%20Liga%20Interregional">2. Liga Interregional</a>, currently the highest tier they reached within the Swiss football pyramid.
Former players include <a href="Elsad%20Zveroti%C4%87">Elsad Zverotic</a> and <a href="Philipp%20Muntwiler">Philipp Muntwiler</a>.
